266
00:13:14,327 --> 00:13:17,730
‐This is sounding good!
‐The fish are ours?

267
00:13:17,730 --> 00:13:20,867
‐As many as we want?
‐Gol'.

268
00:13:20,867 --> 00:13:23,670
Yeah, let's go catch some fish!

269
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:26,105
(cheering)

270
00:13:26,105 --> 00:13:28,374
I'm gonna catch one as
big as Suezo's head!

271
00:13:28,374 --> 00:13:30,843
Why didn't we meet your
friend Undine before?

272
00:13:30,843 --> 00:13:34,847
Undine is shy with
strangers, Tiger.

273
00:13:34,847 --> 00:13:37,984
Oh, but I feel very
safe with Golem.

274
00:13:37,984 --> 00:13:39,619
His friends are mine.

275
00:13:39,619 --> 00:13:42,889
Golem, let's have a
chat before you leave.

276
00:13:42,889 --> 00:13:45,892
Gol', you can meet
all my friends.

277
00:13:45,892 --> 00:13:48,561
This just doesn't
smell right to me.

278
00:13:48,561 --> 00:13:50,330
Oh, Tiger.

279
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:53,633
♪

280
00:13:53,633 --> 00:13:55,635
Oh, wow, this is cool.

281
00:13:55,635 --> 00:13:59,172
'chi, 'chi!

282
00:13:59,172 --> 00:14:02,975
‐Are you a water spirit?
‐Yes, I am, and that's why

283
00:14:02,975 --> 00:14:05,545
Golem's friendship is
so important to me.

284
00:14:05,545 --> 00:14:08,348
I can't leave this lake.

285
00:14:08,348 --> 00:14:10,350
Gol'.

286
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:14,754
Hm, I never dreamed it
would work out so well.

287
00:14:14,754 --> 00:14:16,556
Let me welcome you all.

288
00:14:16,556 --> 00:14:19,392
♪

289
00:14:19,392 --> 00:14:21,227
Welcome!

290
00:14:21,227 --> 00:14:30,136
♪

291
00:14:30,136 --> 00:14:32,638
Yikes, what's going on?

292
00:14:32,638 --> 00:14:34,574
Holly, hang on!

293
00:14:34,574 --> 00:14:38,211
♪

294
00:14:38,211 --> 00:14:39,912
Fishing's over!

295
00:14:39,912 --> 00:14:55,395
♪

296
00:14:55,395 --> 00:14:57,930
Oh no, they'll drown!

297
00:15:02,602 --> 00:15:05,905
Hey guys, are we okay?

298
00:15:05,905 --> 00:15:09,075
Everything's spinnin'
around and around.

299
00:15:09,075 --> 00:15:12,078
Statistically, we're done for!

300
00:15:12,078 --> 00:15:14,814
(evil laughter)

301
00:15:14,814 --> 00:15:16,816
♪

302
00:15:16,816 --> 00:15:19,519
That clinches it, you must
be working for Gray Wolf.

303
00:15:19,519 --> 00:15:20,920
Brilliant,

304
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:23,890
and he sends his best regards.

305
00:15:23,890 --> 00:15:29,028
♪

306
00:15:29,028 --> 00:15:30,763
Torpedo!

307
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:37,503
♪

308
00:15:37,503 --> 00:15:38,638
Tiger!

309
00:15:38,638 --> 00:15:41,040
(laughing)

310
00:15:41,040 --> 00:15:43,943
♪

311
00:15:43,943 --> 00:15:47,780
‐Tiger's in trouble!
‐And around!

312
00:15:47,780 --> 00:15:51,350
Mocchi, fire your cannon
directly into the whirlpool!

313
00:15:51,350 --> 00:16:02,995
♪

314
00:16:02,995 --> 00:16:04,397
Payback!

315
00:16:04,397 --> 00:16:06,098
Torpedo!

316
00:16:06,098 --> 00:16:11,604
♪

317
00:16:11,604 --> 00:16:14,173
‐Bye‐bye!
‐Is everybody okay?

318
00:16:14,173 --> 00:16:17,376
‐That was cool, Mocchi.
‐'chi.

319
00:16:17,376 --> 00:16:20,913
‐I'm still spinning.
‐No you're not.

320
00:16:20,913 --> 00:16:23,749
‐'chi, 'chi!
‐Mocchi, that was great!

321
00:16:23,749 --> 00:16:25,418
Did you drink the whole lake?

322
00:16:25,418 --> 00:16:28,554
(groaning)

323
00:16:28,554 --> 00:16:29,789
Golem!

324
00:16:29,789 --> 00:16:31,457
‐Look!
‐What now?

325
00:16:31,457 --> 00:16:33,392
(chuckling)

326
00:16:33,392 --> 00:16:35,895
You certainly are
a stubborn bunch.

327
00:16:35,895 --> 00:16:38,030
More than you
bargained for, Bubbles?

328
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:41,133
‐More where that came from!
‐You tricked Golem

329
00:16:41,133 --> 00:16:44,470
so you could get
to us, is that it?

330
00:16:44,470 --> 00:16:48,975
That's right, and he was
so easy, I almost feel bad.

331
00:16:48,975 --> 00:16:51,811
(yelling)

332
00:16:51,811 --> 00:16:55,448
♪

333
00:16:55,448 --> 00:16:58,584
Golem?

334
00:16:58,584 --> 00:17:01,220
Gol'.

335
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:03,422
‐Wait!
‐You're not nice.

336
00:17:03,422 --> 00:17:08,594
♪

337
00:17:08,594 --> 00:17:12,965
‐Who's side are you on?
‐Gol'.

338
00:17:12,965 --> 00:17:17,403
‐Undine is my friend.
‐Huh?

339
00:17:17,403 --> 00:17:19,338
She's not, Golem!

340
00:17:19,338 --> 00:17:22,542
‐She's a baddie!
‐She tricked you, Golem!

341
00:17:22,542 --> 00:17:25,645
You've got to believe
me, I'm your friend.

342
00:17:25,645 --> 00:17:28,214
Golem, don't listen.

343
00:17:28,214 --> 00:17:32,785
‐I promised to protect Undine.
‐She's messing with you.

344
00:17:32,785 --> 00:17:37,156
Do not attack my friend.

345
00:17:37,156 --> 00:17:38,524
Stop!

346
00:17:38,524 --> 00:17:40,560
(electric whizzing noise)

347
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,595
(gasping)

348
00:17:42,595 --> 00:17:48,801
♪

349
00:17:48,801 --> 00:17:51,971
Undine, no!

350
00:17:51,971 --> 00:17:55,141
Golem will keep his promise.

351
00:17:55,141 --> 00:17:57,577
They are my enemies, get them!

352
00:17:57,577 --> 00:18:10,957
♪

353
00:18:10,957 --> 00:18:13,726
(fire crackling)

354
00:18:13,726 --> 00:18:17,563
♪

355
00:18:17,563 --> 00:18:19,765
‐Oh no, my oil!
‐Eureka!

356
00:18:19,765 --> 00:18:21,567
Undine's weak point is fire!

357
00:18:21,567 --> 00:18:23,970
Gol'!

358
00:18:23,970 --> 00:18:26,906
(screaming)

359
00:18:26,906 --> 00:18:29,909
‐Gol'!
‐Golem, it's too late!

360
00:18:29,909 --> 00:18:31,911
‐Stop!
‐'chi!

361
00:18:31,911 --> 00:18:35,581
‐Golem!
‐I'm coming, Undine!

362
00:18:35,581 --> 00:18:39,819
♪

363
00:18:39,819 --> 00:18:42,822
‐Why are you doing this?
‐I promised

364
00:18:42,822 --> 00:18:45,191
to protect my new friend.

365
00:18:45,191 --> 00:18:48,794
But after what I've done I don't
deserve your friendship, Golem!

366
00:18:48,794 --> 00:18:51,330
I know, lonely.

367
00:18:51,330 --> 00:18:55,768
♪

368
00:18:55,768 --> 00:18:58,638
You and me soulmates.

369
00:18:58,638 --> 00:19:09,982
♪

370
00:19:09,982 --> 00:19:11,784
Golem, where are you going?

371
00:19:11,784 --> 00:19:14,453
‐Golem!
‐'chi, 'chi, 'chi!

372
00:19:14,453 --> 00:19:17,690
Don't leave us!

373
00:19:17,690 --> 00:19:19,659
Forgive me.

374
00:19:19,659 --> 00:19:22,428
♪

375
00:19:22,428 --> 00:19:24,296
No!

376
00:19:24,296 --> 00:19:26,999
♪

377
00:19:26,999 --> 00:19:29,902
Please forgive me, my deception.

378
00:19:29,902 --> 00:19:32,304
You are true friend.

379
00:19:32,304 --> 00:19:35,041
♪

380
00:19:35,041 --> 00:19:37,777
No, come back!

381
00:19:37,777 --> 00:20:09,108
♪

382
00:20:09,108 --> 00:20:11,744
We'll meet again, Undine,

383
00:20:11,744 --> 00:20:14,714
my soulmate.

384
00:20:14,714 --> 00:20:18,984
Undine wasn't really
a baddie in her heart.

385
00:20:18,984 --> 00:20:23,322
The only weapon that really hit
its mark was Golem's kindness.

386
00:20:23,322 --> 00:20:46,812
♪

387
00:20:46,812 --> 00:20:48,080
♪ Monsters ♪

388
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,648
♪ Monsters rule ♪

389
00:20:49,648 --> 00:21:14,106
♪

390
00:21:14,106 --> 00:21:15,941
♪ Monsters rule ♪

